---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Dongho, The Agent"
  description="Website terms and conditions for Dongho, The Agent."
>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <header>
      <p class="page-kicker">Terms</p>
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: July 13, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <section>
        <h2>Use Of This Website</h2>
        <p>
          By using this website, you agree to use it for lawful purposes and in a way that does not interfere with the website, its hosting, or other visitors.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>General Information Only</h2>
        <p>
          Content on this website is provided for general real estate information and educational purposes. It is not legal, financial, tax, mortgage, or investment advice.
        </p>
        <p>
          Real estate decisions should be made after reviewing your specific situation with qualified professionals.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>No Client Relationship From Website Use</h2>
        <p>
          Visiting this website or submitting a contact form does not automatically create a client, agency, or representation relationship. Any formal real estate relationship must be confirmed through appropriate agreements and required documentation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Accuracy Of Information</h2>
        <p>
          We aim to keep website information helpful and current, but market data, laws, rates, listings, and third-party information can change without notice. We do not guarantee that all content is complete, current, or error-free.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          Website text, layout, images, and branding may not be copied, republished, or reused for commercial purposes without written permission, except where permitted by law.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms may be sent to <a href="mailto:contact@donlee.realtor">contact@donlee.realtor</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
